      "name": "Mesh convergence study — three-level GCI analysis",
      "description": "Grid convergence index analysis across coarse, medium, and fine meshes (4.2M, 9.8M, 21.4M cells). GCI for hemolysis index < 2.1% on fine-to-medium refinement. Discretization uncertainty bounded and acceptable for MRL 2."
    },
    {
