    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to not-assessed status consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Experimental validation shows mean absolute error of 8.3% against FDA pump data, within the 15% acceptance threshold. The UQ campaign, documented in validation result VR-03, confirmed that the hemolysis index acceptance criterion RH < 1 is maintained with 94% probability under combined input uncertainty. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level determination. The decision to accept the model for the stated COU is warranted.",
